{"tid":1550334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"散水歌已響：今天我 寒夜裡看雪飄過","createTime":"2019-09-07T15:34:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T01:28:27.000Z","uid":99962,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3bfecd936b17b36a404d2de86f35143fcadd7ed5","tid":1550334,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:34:12.000Z","msg":"難聽過粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5cee64810f6a6d949993b99ed62963d3d7aaf18","tid":1550334,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:35:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e86a329d9c001acb8e96f83ac842bfb1b528b34e","tid":1550334,"uid":48531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:35:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e9b454b30ec6b4442535e866835d00e4f86911","tid":1550334,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:35:44.000Z","msg":"【逆權運動】周日「人權與民主祈禱會」獲發不反對通知書 遮打集會再往美領館請願"},{"pid":"c8f7172ec6acd2496892b8578b1f2993be787ad4","tid":1550334,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci